/target
.claude/
citizenchain/target

# 根目录 scripts 默认是本机私密脚本区；各产品/模块自己的 scripts 目录允许进 Git。
# 例外：代码生成器/构建工具必须进 Git —— 它们的产出物已在版本管理里，
# 生成器不跟踪就会在模型改名后无声漂移，只能等下次重生时以编译失败爆出来。
# 注意：父目录被排除时 `!` 反选无效，故这里排除的是目录内容 `/scripts/*`。
/scripts/*
!/scripts/generate_citizenapp_governance_registry.mjs
!/scripts/rederive_accounts.py
!/scripts/rebake_china_codes.py
!/scripts/sync-derive-vectors.sh

# 公民控制台是本机私有运维工具（管理部署、Keychain 密钥、Touch ID），整目录不进 Git、不推 GitHub。
/citizenconsole/
target/
citizenchain/citizenui/target/
citizenchain/citizenui/desktop/src-tauri/binaries/
citizenchain/citizenui/desktop/src-tauri/gen/schemas/
citizenchain/nodekey_*
*.sst

# Local chain state
citizenchain/.local-node/

# Frontend build artifacts
citizenchain/node/frontend/dist/

# Python cache
**/__pycache__/
*.pyc

# Local/generated backup files
*.spec*-backup
citizenpassport/.citizenpassport_key
docs/citizenpassport/.citizenpassport_key

# OS / Editor junk
.DS_Store
**/.DS_Store
*.swp
*.tmp
*.log

# IDE local settings
.vscode/
.idea/

# JS/TS local artifacts
**/node_modules/
**/*.tsbuildinfo

# Dart / Flutter generated files
**/.dart_tool/
**/.packages
**/.flutter-plugins
**/.flutter-plugins-dependencies
**/.pub/
**/build/
**/coverage/
.fvm/flutter_sdk
.fvm/versions/

# Flutter iOS generated dependencies
**/ios/Pods/
**/ios/.symlinks/
**/ios/Flutter/ephemeral/
**/ios/Flutter/Generated.xcconfig
**/ios/Flutter/flutter_export_environment.sh

# Flutter Android local/generated files
**/android/.gradle/
**/android/local.properties

# Android 系统错误报告可能包含设备与网络诊断信息，禁止进入仓库。
/bugreport-*.zip

# Android signing secrets
citizenapp/android/key.properties
citizenapp/android/app/*.jks
citizenapp/android/app/*.keystore

# 注册局前端构建产物
citizenchain/registry/frontend/dist/
